Package net.sf.sprockets.google

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Place
    Google Place returned from a Places method.
    Place.Address
    All address components in separate properties.
    Place.Event Deprecated
    the Places API no longer returns events
    Place.Id
    Unique identifier that can be used to retrieve details about a place.
    Place.Id.Filter
    Search or autocomplete filter on place IDs.
    Place.IdPredicate Deprecated
    use Place.Id.Filter instead
    Place.OpeningHours
    Opening and closing times for a day (or span of days) on which a place is open.
    Place.Photo
    Photo for a place that can be downloaded by supplying the reference to Places.photo(Params).
    Place.Prediction
    Place or query that was returned from a Places autocomplete method.
    Place.Review
    Comments and ratings from a Google user.
    Place.Review.Aspect
    Rating for one attribute of a place.
    Places
    Methods for calling Google Places API services.
    Places.Params
    Parameters for Google Places API services.
    Places.Response<T>
    Result from one of the Places methods.
    StreetView
    Method for downloading a Google Street View Image by supplying a lat/long or location name.
    StreetView.Params
    Parameters for the Google Street View Image API service.
    StreetView.Response<T>
    Result from one of the StreetView methods.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Place.Id.Scope
    Availability of a place ID.
    Places.Field
    Fields included in the results of Responses.
    Places.Params.RankBy
    Options for sorting the results.
    Places.Request
    Types of requests that can be sent to the Google Places API service.
    Places.Response.Status
    Indications of the success or failure of the request.
    StreetView.Response.Status
    Indications of the success or failure of the request.
